# Patch owrx/dsp.py
#
# The ModulationValidator regex only allows [a-z0-9\-] in mode names.
# Our modes use underscores (horus_binary, horus_rtty), so we need to
# add underscore to the allowed characters.
#
# In class ModulationValidator, change:
#   RegexValidator(re.compile("^[a-z0-9\\-]+$"))
# To:
#   RegexValidator(re.compile("^[a-z0-9_\\-]+$"))
